replies.body:
As many games as it takes for your MMR to reach Gold IV or V. If you check your OP.GG, and you notice that everyone else in your games are Gold IV or V instead of mid-high Gold or Plat, then that's a good indication that you will be demoted within a few games unless you get your MMR back up to Gold I or Plat level.

Hope this helps :)
